data.description: Back on the market due to buyer’s financing.  Great stater home that has 3 bedroom 1.5 bath in the heart of Brandon! This hidden gem is remodeled and move in ready!  A/C installed August 2017 and Septic piping re-done in 2016. This home features beautiful dark laminate flooring throughout, new stainless appliances, granite counter tops and much more! 140 sqft. detached laundry room w/closet accessible from carport with stand alone a/c, can be used as storage room, guest room or even a man-cave. This beautiful home is in a peaceful neighborhood just minutes from great restaurants, shopping, and entertainment.
